{"tid":921782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［偷食］G記Audit賤男賤女","createTime":"2018-11-30T00:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T14:19:55.000Z","uid":9588,"like":5,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e07d289e7107590c82343464bff11297c297fb30","tid":921782,"uid":9588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:04:12.000Z","msg":"點解Audit咁多賤人, 真係替我朋友覺得委屈, 所以要爆對狗男女既事出來。<br />\n一開始聽我朋友講, 男既欺騙我朋友說自己單身, 後來知道原來一直呃住佢： ＂其實我有女朋友，只不過我跟她分唔到手&hellip;&hellip;＂＂可唔可以同左我一齊先，等她一完成考試後，我就會立即跟她分手 ，今次我一定可以分到，我唔可以無左你&hellip;＂bababa&hellip;<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;一個大話連篇的人<br />\n其實一開始都有叫我朋友唔好，一個人性格係咁, 邊有可能會改變，但邊有可能會肯聽。<br />\n男的和他前任分左手後幾個月, 我朋友想比機會男的, 所以一齊左, 但一齊後幾個月後覺得大家唔合適, 所以決定分手, 男的竟然同佢既好同事係背後不繼數落我朋友, 欲加之罪, 何患無辭&hellip;點解會有人咁賤。<br />\n而我朋友分手之後, 一句男的壞話都没有無講過。<br />\n不過我朋友心軟，比男的說服左一齊返, 男的話會改過, 會對我朋友好好的, 之前講的所有都係一時之氣。<br />\n直到有一日我朋友真係崩潰左，因為發現男的一直都利用緊我朋友的信任&hellip; <br />\n出job真係一對情侣最大的考驗 (peak season一隻寶馬job) &hellip;&hellip;<br />\n因為男的會認為没有人知道的情況下&hellip;&hellip;對我朋友做出不忠既行為, 都無從追究, 我朋友話由之前定時定候報到, 變到有幾晚唔見左, 由零晨打電話打到朝早比男的都唔聽, 第二日先覆返, 男的既借口永遠都係工作太忙, 唔記得左報到 (不如直接話, happy到唔記得左我朋友的存在), 無奈地我朋友都選擇相信男的。<br />\n荒謬到男的竟然同我朋友講, 要同同事返大陸酒店房睇波, 正常人聽到都覺得奇怪, 咁多地方睇波唔去, 係都要返大陸酒店, 男的又發我朋友難渣話管住, 只好比男的去, 就咁2男2女上左深圳 &rdquo;睇波&rdquo;。 順理成章, 返大陸依段時間又係搵唔到人&hellip;<br />\n到有一日我朋友見到男的同他朋友的msg, 終於確定自己一直都無諗多&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTzUdjH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTzUdjH.png&h=dc6fe1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmqzXMn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmqzXMn.png&h=dc0b04dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再睇埋對狗男女的對話&hellip;到底出job的時候瞓左幾多次&hellip;搞左幾多次&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbfHndS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbfHndS.png&h=0ba3ce81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WORfHdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWORfHdS.png&h=cf726234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NeXVyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NeXVyS.png&h=9c1dbaaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWv8hWo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWv8hWo.png&h=e3eb26fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SSSiE0x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSSSiE0x.png&h=8e62af6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFwSKsc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFwSKsc.png&h=575ef598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3cZpJ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3cZpJ4.png&h=18fc6ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GtYmCNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtYmCNd.png&h=7bf48630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RsKha7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsKha7d.png&h=624aab2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CeXVyT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CeXVyT.png&h=c8585cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我朋友說仲見到個女拍男的瞓教片&hellip;.出job應該瞓過無數次啦<br />\n點解人地女朋友係公司都可以做人第三者, 面皮厚到&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvvDE0R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvvDE0R.png&h=64718380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyhVHeb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyhVHeb.png&h=28624133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJO54BG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJO54BG.png&h=74ffaf64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7Qsymi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7Qsymi.png&h=c73bd43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGF0Tmi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGF0Tmi.png&h=5b901ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解可以成日借住同job話無野呢?<br />\n我朋友除了發現男的和同事有路, 仲發現有同事介紹自己朋友比男的 (傻的嗎), 仲一堆街外人)&hellip;.發現之後, 男的求我朋友原諒, 知道自己做錯左了, 如果知什麼是錯對, 會有今日?<br />\n過幾日男的又搵藉口話想自己一個人, 要分手, 唔係想同第二個一齊&hellip;係想自己一個人喎, 到底各式各樣既藉口可以有幾多&hellip;<br />\n其實周圍的人都知男的一直都有溝緊A1的囡囡&hellip;<br />\n男的之前仲有溝緊2017年batch既幾個A1, 但人地醒目, 知男的有女朋友就立即停左, 但仲要日日去聊人地&hellip;.<br />\n男的依家已經著手溝緊, 啱啱個新入來既2018年batch A1bb&hellip; <br />\n朋友話有時明知男的係咁, 唔揭發男的, 係想男的有一日會真正地知自己做錯, 可惜男的唔會有這一日&hellip; 所以公司的囡囡要小心喇。"},{"pid":"939b57959e69599d0733f83fbafdc203d05e026e","tid":921782,"uid":186087,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:07:46.000Z","msg":"太長。無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5565874ef9da3ddcaf0d60a9ea5b4a4862c9f6f1","tid":921782,"uid":57079,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩<br />\n<br />\n利申：睇唔明殘體字"},{"pid":"1dc8f8a92713ef0243cb6bbc9e6b68a232d34298","tid":921782,"uid":142205,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:09:45.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521d9f0a8b4c845474bd920dc03f9cf0b084512d","tid":921782,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"Too long 唔撚read"},{"pid":"b023aaacacba69d37ff77d96a353c7b3e1c862f8","tid":921782,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"世界太淫亂"},{"pid":"649ab7c6a6c5c71a1f37833dae456d33da9afd26","tid":921782,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:14:38.000Z","msg":"出圖啦"},{"pid":"b71a237d002c03db6127d66cc4e59251867b1fb2","tid":921782,"uid":146435,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00